entries.femaleVariant: What are the roots that clutch... what branches grow... out of this stony rubbish?
Son of man... You cannot say, or guess, for you know only... A heap of broken images...

Where the sun beats... 
And the dead tree gives no shelter... the cricket no relief... And the dry stone... no sound of water...
Only...! Ekhe, Ekhe...! There is shadow under this red rock...
Come in under the shadow of this red rock!
And I will show you... something different from either your shadow at morning striding behind you... or your shadow at evening rising to meet you!
I will show you fear in a handful of dust!
